---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ryan Chibana" description="Senior software engineer at Block working on data infrastructure, observability, and compliance systems. Previously at Cruise, Yelp, and Epic.">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Hey, I'm Ryan.</h1>
    <p>
      I'm a senior software engineer based in Carmel, Indiana. I currently work at Block. Most of my career has been spent building production data infrastructure — pipelines, observability systems, and platform tooling that other teams depend on.
    </p>

    <p>
      Before Block, I worked at Cruise on ML infrastructure for autonomous vehicles, and spent five years at Yelp building and scaling data pipelines. Before that, I was at Epic Systems. I studied CS at Indiana University and later completed a Master's at Georgia Tech in Interactive Intelligence.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm most interested in ML platform engineering and agentic AI systems. Outside of work, I play piano, guitar, and bass. I also enjoy reading and am a bit of a film buff.
    </p>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/chibanaryan">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ryanchibana">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="mailto:chibana.ryan@gmail.com">Email</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 36rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
